August 11, 2020: The Los Santos Summer Special Update

  • The Los Santos Summer Special has arrived, bringing many updates and additions to GTA Online, including the following:
    Galaxy Super Yachts Co-op Missions
    Business Battles (In New Locations)
    Diamond Casino & Resort Adversary Modes
    New Open Wheel Races
    12+ New Vehicles & Customizations
    Open Wheel Race Creator
    General Improvements & Fixes
    & More
  • Galaxy Super Yacht owners will be able to take part in six brand new co-op missions for 1-4 players. Missions will include high-speed adventures, deep-sea diving, and more, and interested players can take part from the bridge of their ship or from their iFruit phone.
  • Players who host and complete all six missions will unlock a unique “sea-faring” outfit.
  • Nine new Open Wheel race tracks have been added, including the following:
    Land Act Dam
    RON Alternates Windfarm
    & more
  • Refinements have been made to Open Wheel gameplay, including the following:
    Players can now change tire types while pitting
    New visible tire wear indicators
    New body damage indicators
    Players who drive the wrong way or stay stationary for too long will be ghosted for other drivers
    & more
advertisement
  • An Open Wheel Race Creator has also been added, so interested players will be able to use over 60 props to create their dream courses.
  • Newly revamped Business Battles are now cropping up in new places with greatly amplified rewards.
  • Players who win a Business Battle between now and Aug. 19 will earn the following (in addition to their other rewards):
    Pink Dot Tech Mask
  • The Diamond Casino & Resort now also plays host to eight different modes through the Diamond Adversary Series, including the following:
    Every Bullet Counts
    Slasher
    Hardest Target
    Resurrection
    & more.
  • Players will also notice low-level drug deals taking place all over the city, so keep an eye out for suspicious vehicles and activities.
  • A new set of collectibles is now available from Solomon Richards. Players will receive a phone call from Richards when they log in. He will task them with retrieving his 10 lost movie props. Returning them to him will earn the player a special reward.
  • The following vehicles have been added to GTA Online:
    Invetero Coquette D10
    Lampadati Tigon
    Declasse DR1
    Vapid Peyote Custom
    Benefactor BR8
    Imponte Beater Dukes
    Albany Manana Custom
    Canis Seminole Frontier
    Bravado Youga Classic 4X4
    Dundreary Landstalker XL
    Benefactor Glendale Custom
    BF Club
    Maibatsu Penumbra FF
    Bravado Gauntlet Classic Custom
    Declasse Yosemite Rancher
  • Additionally, new upgrades at Benny’s Original Motor Works, and more, are now available.
  • Additionally, 15 new types of Off-Road Wheels, 30 new sets of Street Wheels, and new tire designs have been added to modification shops around the city.
  • Two new arcade cabinets have been added including Liberty city classic “QUB3D” and “Axe of Fury.” “Street Crimes: Gang Wars” can now also be played as a single-player game, pitting them against AI. Players interested in purchasing those cabinets should head to their Arcade Laptop and pick them up from Pixel Emporium.
  • Hundreds of new clothing items have also been added to celebrate the arrival of summer. Interested players should head to their local Southern San Andreas and Blaine County stores.
  • Earn Double Rewards (GTA$, RP) by participating in the following:
    A Superyacht Life
    Open Wheel Races
    Diamond Adversary Series

August 7, 2020: The Los Santos Summer Special Update Announcement

  • This week, Rockstar revealed the Los Santos Summer Special, which arrives on August 11.
  • The Los Santos Summer Special will bring the following to GTA Online:
    Galaxy Super Yachts Co-op Missions
    Business Battles (In New Locations)
    Diamond Casino & Resort Adversary Modes
    New Open Wheel Races
    12+ New Vehicles & Customizations
    Open Wheel Race Creator
    General Improvements & Fixes
    & More
  • Galaxy Super Yacht owners will be able to take part in brand new co-op missions for 1-4 players. Missions will include high-speed adventures, deep-sea diving, and more.
  • Players will also be able to take part in new Business Battles, which will crop up in strange new places.
  • The Diamond Casino & Resort will play host to intense Adversary Battles once the Los Santos Summer Update arrives.
  • Additionally, over a dozen new vehicles will arrive, including off-road vehicles, customizable sports cars, and new Open Wheel cars, as well.
  • A new series of Open Wheel races will also be added, as will a brand new Open Wheel Race Creator.
  • Rockstar also announced more general improvements and fixes will arrive with the update and, of course, a slew of special events and bonuses in the coming weeks, not to mention the biggest GTA Online update ever later this year.

Dec. 12, 2019: The Diamond Casino Heist

This week in Grand Theft Auto Online, Rockstar announced the arrival of the Diamond Casino Heist update.

  • Players can now participate in The Diamond Casino Heist in Grand Theft Auto Online.

While the Diamond Casino has been taken over by the Duggans, players will have the opportunity to team up with Georgina Cheng to plan and execute a heist to take them for all they’re worth, stealing everything from the Diamond’s vault.

  • Players can obtain the new Arcade Business property by meeting Lester in Mirror Park, which will house the following playable games:
    Badlands Revenge II
    The Wizard’s Ruin
    Race and Chase: Street Legal
    Race and Chase - Get Truckin’
    Space Monkey 3: Bananas Gone Bad
    Shiny Wasabi Kitty Claw
    Nazar Speaks Fortune Teller
    The Love Professor
    Defender of the Faith (Degenatron Classic)
    Monkey’s Paradise (Degenatron Classic)
    Penetrator (Degenatron Classic)

  • While the Arcade operates on the ground level, the basement is where the heist will be planned and practiced. The basement hideout contains three planning boards, a place for getaway vehicles, and items you will need to perpetrate and practice the heist, itself.
  • Players will be able to purchase the following Arcade Upgrades through the laptop in the Arcade Management Office:
    Master Control Terminal
    Drone Station
  • The following Arcade features are also available:
    Jukebox
    Bar Area
    Television
    Safe
advertisement
  • Players will also be able to purchase the following Heist items:
    Casino Model
    Fake Vault Door
    Door Keypad
  • Players will also need to gather a crew, which they can gather by tapping Lester’s criminal contacts.

  • Players will be able to choose between three approaches, from which to begin the heist, including:
    Silent and Sneaky
    The Big Con
    Aggressive
  • Players choosing Silent and Sneaky will aim to get in and out with the money, without alerting anyone.
  • Players choosing The Big Con will attempt to infiltrate the casino and use their insider influence to give themselves an edge.

Completing The Big Con approach will also unlock a new weapon for purchase from Ammu-Nation: the Vom Feuer Ceramic Pistol.

  • Players choosing Aggressive will use straight force to attempt to take what they want, then blaze a path to the exit.

Regardless of the approach players pick, they will have plenty of choices to make along the way, and if they fail in their approach, they can still roll with the punches, change the plan on the fly, and succeed.

  • As part of the Heist update, this week the following vehicles has been added to GTA Online via Legendary Motorsport and Southern San Andreas Super Autos:
    Karin Everon (Heist)
    Lampadati Komoda (Heist)
    Maxwell Asbo (Heist)
    Maxwell Vagrant (Heist)
    Vapid Retinue MKII (Heist)
    Ubermacht Rebla GTS (SUV)
  • The following vehicles has been added to GTA Online via Warstock Cache & Carry:
    MTL Fire Truck
    Declasse Bugstars Burrito
    Gruppe Sechs branded Brute Stockade
    LS Water & Power branded Brute Boxville
    Declasse Lifeguard Truck
    Nagazaki Blazer Lifeguard

Players will also be able to tune into the new Danny Brown-hosted iFruit Radio station starting today.

  • 50 Signal Jammers have appeared around the world of GTA Online, and players who destroy them all will gain access to an expert hacker. Lester will contact the player after destroying the first one, and destroying them all will award a new Heist asset, as well as GTA$ and RP.
  • The Los Santos Slasher is still at large, taking out victim after victim with an old Navy Revolver, but clever players will be able to find 5 clues hidden around the map. After gathering each clue, the killer will be unlocked, and will emerge when the player is vulnerable. Taking the killer out will unlock the Navy Revolver for them, free of charge.

Grand Theft Auto Online

Taking the fundamental concepts of open-world freedom, ambient activity and mission-based gameplay of the Grand Theft Auto series and making them available to multiple players in an incredibly dynamic online world, GTA Online offers the freedom to explore alone or work cooperatively with friends to complete missions.

Rockstar North, Rockstar Games

Thor: Love and Thunder Trailer

Check out the teaser trailer for Marvel Studios' Thor: Love and Thunder, starring Chris Hemsworth, Christian Bale, Tessa Thompson, Taika Waititi, and Natalie Portman. Thor (Chris Hemsworth) goes on a journey unlike anything he's ever faced - a quest for inner peace. But his retirement is interrupted by a galactic killer known as Gorr the God Butcher (Christian Bale), who seeks the extinction of the gods. To combat the threat, Thor enlists the help of King Valkyrie (Tessa Thompson), Korg (Taika Waititi) and ex-girlfriend Jane Foster (Natalie Portman), who - to Thor's surprise - inexplicably wields his magical hammer, Mjolnir, as the Mighty Thor. Together, they embark upon a harrowing cosmic adventure to uncover the mystery of the God Butcher's vengeance and stop him before it's too late.
